JComponent getComponent()

      • layoutComponent

        default void layoutComponent()
        Update the component's size. Called by EditorComponentLayoutManager when the editor component is being laid out. If the cell size should change as a result, call EditorCell.requestRelayout().

        The default implementation validates the component, then sets the component size to its preferred size if it differs.
